      "role": "user",
      "content": "i think i get the absolute value part. but i'm having a hard time visualizing why the L1 penalty actually hits zero while L2 just gets really small. is there some kind of intuitive way to think about the geometry of the penalty terms that explains why one \"cuts off\" features and the other doesn't?",
